sh functions} and \\emph{$\\varepsilon$-synchronization hash\nfunctions}. We believe our techniques can have further applications in the\nliterature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2018 16:24:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Apr 2018 00:44:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 20 Apr 2018 03:54:48 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2018 04:06:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-18"}
