s like\nfibre cross-talk, and reliably extracts spectra with a resolution $\\sim2.3$\ntimes above the nominal resolution of the instrument. Our rigorous treatment of\noptical aberrations also encourages a less conservative spectrograph design in\nthe future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2018 18:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-22"}
