icant proper motion of VLA 1623\nusing our observations and those in the literature. This result indicates that\nthe proper motion of nearby systems must be corrected for when combining ALMA\ndata from different epochs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2018 22:57:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2018 13:10:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 20:12:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-13"}
